{
  "id": "61e91b386bf112001df5f232",
  "title": "(3.4.2) Learn more after testing",
  "created": 1549701014,
  "updated": 1553591055,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "61e91b38aff09e0000786fd9",
      "text": "(3.4.2) Learn more after testing",
      "created": 1549701014,
      "updated": 1553591022,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "61e91b38aff09e0000786fda",
      "text": "If you [review] after the [test], your memory is further enhanced. In the psychologist [Karpicke and Blunt]'s experiments (*18), 80 college students have read the texts related to science and conducted a test to test their understanding in a week. Subjects were divided into three groups, and each studied in different ways. (*19)",
      "created": 1549701014,
      "updated": 1549786120,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "61e91b38aff09e0000786fdb",
      "text": "",
      "created": 1549701014,
      "updated": 1549701014,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "61e91b38aff09e0000786fdc",
      "text": "\tOnetime learning group: Groups that read the texts only once",
      "created": 1549701014,
      "updated": 1549701040,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "61e91b38aff09e0000786fdd",
      "text": "\tRepeated learning group: Groups that read the texts 4 times",
      "created": 1549701014,
      "updated": 1549701041,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "61e91b38aff09e0000786fde",
      "text": "\tRecalling group: Group that",
      "created": 1549701014,
      "updated": 1549701042,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "61e91b38aff09e0000786fdf",
      "text": "\t\tread textbooks once,",
      "created": 1549701014,
      "updated": 1549701043,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "61e91b38aff09e0000786fe0",
      "text": " \ttry to recall, ",
      "created": 1549701014,
      "updated": 1549701014,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "61e91b38aff09e0000786fe1",
      "text": "\t\tthen read the texts again,",
      "created": 1549701014,
      "updated": 1549701051,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "61e91b38aff09e0000786fe2",
      "text": " \tand try to recall. ",
      "created": 1549701014,
      "updated": 1549701053,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "61e91b38aff09e0000786fe3",
      "text": "",
      "created": 1549701014,
      "updated": 1549701014,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "61e91b38aff09e0000786fe4",
      "text": "The accuracy rate of the onetime learning group was about 30%, and the repeated learning group was higher than that by about 50%. This difference is nothing special that memory by reading four times is stronger than reading once. However, what is important is the record of the recalling group. This group had an even higher 70% correct answer rate. Rather than repeating the input 4 times, it was better to use a part of the time for the tests.",
      "created": 1549701014,
      "updated": 1549701060,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "61e91b38aff09e0000786fe5",
      "text": "",
      "created": 1549701014,
      "updated": 1549701014,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "61e91b38aff09e0000786fe6",
      "text": "---",
      "created": 1553591048,
      "updated": 1553591050,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
